---
title: Vegetarian Burrito Bowl with Salsa, Crispy Black Beans, and Monterey Jack
description: Step aside, plates. These days, it’s all about bowl-tastic dinners. This one’s overflowing with warm brown rice and slightly crisp black beans. And don’t worry, we definitely didn’t forget about the cheese. Squeeze some lime over the top and you’ll be good to go.
